name: dunamai
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "dunamai" %}
{% set version = "1.12.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fac4f09e2b8a105bd01f8c50450fea5aa489a6c439c949950a65f0dd388b0d20

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - dunamai = dunamai.__main__:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - poetry-core >=1.0.0
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - importlib-metadata >=1.6.0
    - packaging >=20.9
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - dunamai
  commands:
    - pip check
    - dunamai --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/mtkennerly/dunamai
  summary: Dynamic version generation
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - BastianZim
